    <tr>
        <td colspan="5"><b><font size="-1" color="#333333" style="display: block !important; padding: 20px 0 5px !important;">优设哥向您推荐：</font></b></td>
    </tr>
    
        <tr>
                <td width="102" valign="top" style="padding: 5px !important; margin: 0 !important;">
                    <a target="_blank" title="简约不简单！带你重新审视正在流行的卡片式设计趋势" style="text-decoration: none !important; cursor: pointer !important;" href="http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uisdc.com%2Fcard-based-design-trend&from=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.uisdc.com%2Fminimalism-web-design-principle">
                        <img style="margin: 0 !important; padding: 2px !important; border: 1px solid #DDDDDD !important; width: 96px !important; height: 96px !important;" src="http://wumii-cc.wumii.cn/site_images/ti/131WT1wtk.jpg?i=LK5zpAXf" width="96px" height="96px" /><br />
